name: Dust Bowl Brown Dobby Blouse - Blythe
description:
The dobby blouse has become a SqueakyMonkey classic... Introducing a new color, Dust Bowl Brown! Well, not so new as I dyed the fabric years ago. ;)

A gorgeous soft hand-dyed brown dobby blouse that has been waiting to happen for 5 years until the right coordinate came along. 

The blouse fabric is dyed and has varying tones of a dusty brown... 

Fabric has been treated to deter staining your doll... 

This is a pre-order for May 2013 production. Please keep this in mind when ordering.

name: Monster High Distressed Jeans
description:
Your Monster was born in these jeans, and she's worn them nearly to pieces (at least she would like to think so).

The distressed jeans have a snug fit and sit on the hips to avoid a bulky "Soccer Mom" look around the waist. Tiny detailed stitching (including faux front pockets and zipper) is completed before the jeans are distressed.

A lot of time and experimentation (and yes! painful mistakes along the way) have gone into perfecting these tiny distressed jeans.

Jeans will vary as they are all unique. The process to make these little gems is very tedious and time consuming and only done a few times a year. Due to the nature of the process - each pair is unique.

Fabric/care details: Jeans are 100% cotton, Machine washable. Minimal Machine Drying is good - finish by Air Dry to prevent shrinkage.

Just like people jeans these jeans need to be stretched out a little after washing. In other words - they'll be a little tight when your doll first puts them on - but, they stretch out with wear.

This is for the jeans only. Doll, shoes, shirts, accessories not included.

Ready to ship!
